ygData.subject: Re: Executioner Hood vs BI Crown
ygData.msgSnippet: Na, he didn t spawn with a weapon at all. He was just too tough, like I said the casters spells were resisted and it only left a bard, Paladin & a level 46
ygData.messageBody:
Na, he didn't spawn with a weapon at all. He was just too tough, like I
said the casters spells were resisted and it only left a bard, Paladin & a
level 46 necro's pet +1 lvl 50 healer to finish him off, there was no
chance.





"Sylly Songsynger" <jgs@...> on 16/02/2000 15:15:35

Sylly
